qas.question: What institution aids in the creation of charter schools in New York?

answers.text: New York City Charter School Center

qas.question: About how many private schools does New York have?

context: The <a0_0>New York City Charter School Center<a0_0/> assists the setup of new charter schools. There are approximately <a1_0>900<a1_0/> additional privately run secular and religious schools in the city.
